# Baseline allowlist for the file-prefix convention enforced by
# scripts/check-php-helper-prefix.sh — see CONVENTIONS.md and
# PLAN_pre_release_followup.md § T2.8.
#
# Format: <repo-relative path>:<_helper_name> (one per line). Comments
# start with # and are ignored.
#
# These 24 entries were captured 2026-05-15 when the check landed —
# they're the existing offenders, grandfathered. Going forward, the
# convention applies strictly to new helpers: rename to include the
# file stem rather than appending here.
#
# Tracked follow-up: rename pass over this allowlist in a focused PR
# post-v1.0.0 (per project_pr_mode_after_v1).

# --- gauge_search.php (stem: gauge_search) -----------------------------
